{"id": "pos029", "name": "Audio_Hospital_694_03_28", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Daniel! Wait up!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Sorry... I don't know what's wrong with me.\nI need some space. Leave me alone, okay.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "I, I'll be with you...\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "I said leave me alone!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "Running"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Ah! Daniel......! Waah!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Crash"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Are you alright? Oh, is that you, Clara? What's the matter?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "No, nothing. We're here to visit Aroma. Here, your phone. Sorry about that.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No need to worry. Do be more careful in the hallways though.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "Running"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Daniel!</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... Sorry, someone ran into me just now. The preparations, they're all set, right?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Researcher A]"], "content": "<i>Yes. One word from director and we can begin the operation at any time.</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Good, but stay alert. This operation must only be carried out in secret.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Researcher A]"], "content": "<i>Understood. For our aspirations.</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Arnold, this is no longer just for our aspirations anymore.\nAroma getting involved in this kind of thing... I can't accept it. I will save her no matter what. I still need to properly apologize to her...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Researcher A]"], "content": "<i>Director...?</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No, it's nothing... In short, I will leave this operation to you guys.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Researcher A]"], "content": "<i>One more thing, about Helena...</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I'll figure out a way to convince her.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Researcher A]"], "content": "<i>She should be able to understand as well...</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Yes. I won't allow anything to happen to Aroma again. We have to make sure she lives no matter what.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Researcher A]"], "content": "<i>Absolutely!</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Then that's it for now.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Call Ends]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena... Ah! Iris, it's been a while. Are you here to visit Aroma?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Yes, I'm here to bring her the academic schedule. Ah, is there something important you want to discuss with sis Helena? It's about time I take my leave too. I will not disturb you guys.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No need to be so modest. Please come visit more often. Aroma will be very glad to see you. Oh right; about your two classmates, I just saw them run away in a hurry.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Those two... I'll go catch them. Thank you!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah, Aroma reacted to her classmates just now. That's a great sign!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Really? That's good to hear.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "With this progress, the surgery will definitely be successful too. Aroma will come back to us very soon...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Ah, I have to discuss something with the doctor...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena! About the surgery next month...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... I'm still against it. A.R.C. is still months, even years away from completing the recreation of that technology. Yet they decide to rush and let the hospital run trials with it.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "This again... With Aroma's current situation, we can't afford to waste any time arguing about this.\nPlus, We signed the contract already. What else are you going to do?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Maybe we should seriously consider going with what I proposed...?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Stop bringing that up! Why on earth would I agree to that!? That project of yours was already discontinued by A.R.C. \nYou've gone insane!\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "You're the one who's gone insane! Compare to me, you rather trust that worthless doctor!?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "I......!\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I already saw through him. Even if that technology actually works, that useless hack doesn't have anywhere near the skills to pull it off! It's way too risky! \nI'm not handing Aroma's life over to someone who'll undoubtedly mess up!\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma is my little sister! I will decide who I want to save her life!\nThis is none of your business! Now p*** off!\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">I... I want to save her even more than you do...</font>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Daniel！待って！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "悪い……俺どうかしてるんだ。\n一人にしてくれ。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "私、あなたのそばに……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "一人にしてくれって言ってるだろ！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "あっ！Daniel……！わぁ！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "ぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "大丈夫かい？\n君は、Claraちゃん？どうしたの？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "いえ、大丈夫です。\nAromaに会いに来たんです。\nこれ…Noahさんの電話……すみません……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "気にしないで。\n気を付けるんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Daniel！</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……すまない。\n人とぶつかってしまってね。\n準備はできてるね？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>はい。\nチーフの指示さえあれば、すぐに実行できます。</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "分かった。\nくれぐれも気を付けるんだ。\nこれは内密に進める必要がある。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>はい。\n私たちの理想のために。</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Arnold、これはもはや僕たちの理想だけでは収まらないものだ。\nAromaちゃん……こんなことは……僕には受け入れることはできない。\n必ずあの子を救ってみせる。ちゃんと謝るためにも……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>チーフ……？</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "いや、なんでもない……\nとにかく、今回のことは頼んだよ。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>そういえば、Helenaさんは……</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "僕が説得する。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>きっと分かってくれるはずです……</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あぁ、Aromaちゃんにこれ以上危険が及ぶことは僕が許さない。\n必ず…必ず僕があの子を生かしてみせる。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>おっしゃる通りです！</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "じゃあ、ひとまずこれで。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話終了]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……あっ！Irisちゃん、久しぶりだね。\nAromaに会いに来てくれたのかい？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "はい。授業のノートを届けに。\nあ、何かお話があるんですよね？\nじゃあ、私は帰りますね。\nお邪魔になっちゃうと悪いし。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "いや、気にしなくていいんだよ。\nまた、会いにきてやってね。\nAromaも喜ぶから。\nそうだ！お友達2人がさっきバタバタ走って行ったよ。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "まったくもう……私追いかけますね！\nありがとうございました！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah！\nさっきクラスメイトの子たちが話しかけたら、Aromaに少し反応があったのよ！\nよかった……本当に……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "本当かい？それはよかった。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "これなら、手術も必ず成功するわ。\nAromaにもうすぐ会える……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あっ、私先生とお話しする約束を……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena！来月の手術のことなんだけど……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……僕はやっぱり反対だ。\nあの技術をA.R.C.はまだ使いこなせていない。\nにもかかわらず、病院に使わせて……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "またなの……Aromaの状態は一刻を争うのよ。\nもう同意書にもサインしたじゃない。\nなら、どうしろって言うの？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "僕の提案について、もう一度よく考えてくれないか……？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "もうその話はしないで！\n私が頷くわけがないでしょう！\nあなたのその研究はA.R.C.によって廃止されてるのよ！？\nあなた、狂ってる！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "狂ってるのは君だ！\n僕よりも、あんな無能な医者を信じるというのか！？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "私は……！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "僕はとっくに見抜いていたよ。\nたとえあれが役に立ったとしても、あの医者にはそもそもの技術がない！\n危険すぎる！\nAromaちゃんの命をあんな奴に預けることはできない！\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aromaは私の妹なのよ！\nあの子の命を誰に預けるかは、私が決めるわ！\nどこかへ行ってちょうだい！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">僕は……君よりよほどあの子を救いたいと思っているんだ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Daniel！等等啦！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "對不起……我不知道我怎麼了，讓我一個人靜一靜。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "我陪你……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "我說讓我一個人啦！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊！Daniel……！哇！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳還好嗎？這不是 Clara 嗎？你們怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "不，沒事，我們來看 Aroma。來，你的電話，對不起。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "沒關係，小心點吶。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Daniel！</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……抱歉，剛剛被人撞到了。都安排好了吧？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>是，只要主任一聲令下，我們隨時可以開始行動。</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好，小心點。這件事只能祕密進行。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>知道，為了我們的理想。</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Arnold，這已經不僅僅是為了我們的理想了。Aroma 遇到這種事……我不能接受，我一定會救她，我……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>主任……？</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不，沒什麼……總之這件事拜託你們了。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>對了，Helena 姐那邊……</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我會想辦法說服她的。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>她應該也能理解的……</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯，我不會讓 Aroma 再出任何事，我們一定要讓她活下去。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[研究員 A]"], "content": "<i>當然！</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "那就先這樣。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話結束]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……啊！Iris 好久不見，來看 Aroma 嗎？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "嗯，來拿教學進度給她。啊、你們要談事情嗎？我也差不多要走了，不打擾你們。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不會不會，有空常來，Aroma 會很開心的。對了，妳的兩個同學剛剛匆匆忙忙跑走了喔。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "真是的……我去追他們，謝謝！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah，剛剛 Aroma 對同學們有反應耶，太好了！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "真的啊？太棒了。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "這樣手術一定也能很成功，Aroma 很快就會回來……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，我得去找醫生討論……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena！下個月的手術……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我還是反對。那項技術 A.R.C. 根本還沒還原完整就趕鴨子上架給醫院試用了。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "又來了……Aroma 的情況已經刻不容緩，合約都簽了，你要怎樣？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "還是認真考慮我說的那件事吧……？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "別再跟我說這個了！我怎麼可能答應！？你那個項目已經被 A.R.C. 廢止了，你根本瘋了！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳才瘋了！比起我，妳寧願相信那種庸醫嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我……！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我早就看穿他了，就算那東西有用，那傢伙根本沒有技術！太危險了！我不會把 Aroma 的性命交給那種人開玩笑！\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma 是我妹妹！她的性命要交給誰拯救輪不到你來決定！給我滾！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我比妳……更想救她啊……</font>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Daniel! 기다려!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "미안... 모르겠어. 나도 왜 이러는 건지. 혼자 있게 해줘.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "나도 함께...\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "혼자 있게 해달라고!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "달려간다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "아! Daniel....! 아얏!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "괜찮니? 너는... Clara? 너희들 무슨 일이니?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "아, 아무것도 아니에요. \nAroma를 보러 왔어요. 아, 여기 핸드폰이요. 죄송합니다.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "괜찮다. 조심하거라.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "달려간다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Daniel!</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "...미안하군. 방금 다른 사람이랑 부딪히는 바람에. 전부 준비됐어?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[연구원 A]"], "content": "<i>네. 주임님이 지시만 내리시면 즉각 실행할 수 있도록 준비해뒀습니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "좋다.\n조심히 가보자고. 이 일은 비밀로 진행되는 일이니까.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[연구원 A]"], "content": "<i>알겠습니다.\n우리들의 이상을 위해.</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Arnold, 이건 우리들의 이상을 위해서가 아니다. Aroma의 일은... 난 아직도 받아들이지 못했어. 난 꼭 그 애를 구하고 말 거다. 그리고 진심으로 사과할 거고...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[연구원 A]"], "content": "<i>주임님...?</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아니야, 아무것도... 어쨌든 이번엔 너희들에게 신세 좀 지겠다.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[연구원 A]"], "content": "<i>아, Helena 씨가 저쪽에...</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "내가 설득해보지.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[연구원 A]"], "content": "<i>아마도 이해해주실 겁니다...</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "응. Aroma에게 또 그런 일이 생겨선 절대 안 돼.. 반드시... 반드시 살려내야 해.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[연구원 A]"], "content": "<i>말씀대로입니다!</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그래. 알겠으면 일단 여기까지 하도록 하지.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[통화 종료]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……아! 오랜만이구나 Iris. Aroma를 보러 온 거니?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "네. 그리고 이번 달 수업 진도 내용도 전해줄 겸 왔어요. 두 분 말씀 나누세요. 방해되지 않도록 전 먼저 가보도록 하겠습니다.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아니야. 시간 나면 자주 와주렴. Aroma도 분명 기뻐할 테니깐. 아, 그런데  방금 다른 두 친구들은 엄청 다급하게 뛰어가고 있던데.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "어휴 정말이지…… 지금 따라가볼게요. 감사합니다!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah, 방금 Aroma가 반 친구들에게 반응을 보였어! 정말 다행이야...\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "정말? \n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "이 정도면 수술은 분명 성공한 거나 다름없어. Aroma도 금방 옛날 모습으로 돌아올 거야...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "그래! 의사 선생님이랑 당장 얘기해봐야겠어...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena! 다음 달 수술...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "...난 반대 입장이야. 그 기술은 A.R.C.에서도 완벽하게 검증을 끝내지 않은 상태로 의료업계 측에 테스트용으로 팔아먹은 기술이거든.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "또 그런다... Aroma는 지금 일각도 지체할 수 없는 상황이라고. 동의서에도 이미 사인했고. 그럼 어떻게 하려고?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "전에 내가 말했던 거, 다시 제대로 생각해보는 건...?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "그 얘긴 다시 꺼내지도 마! \n내가 찬성할 거라고 생각해? \n당신의 그 연구는 A.R.C.에서도 이미 폐기해버렸잖아! 당신은 미쳤어!\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "너야말로 미쳤어! 나보다 그런 돌팔이 의사가 더 신뢰가 간다 이 말이야!?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "나는...!\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "난 진작에 알아봤다고. \n비록 그게 도움이 될 수 있을진 몰라도, 그 녀석의 기술은 형편없이 돌팔이라는 걸 말이야. Aroma의 목숨을 그런 사람에게 맡긴다고? 진심으로 그렇게 생각하는 거야!?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma는 내 동생이야!\n내 동생 목숨을 구해줄 사람을 당신이 뭔데 멋대로 결정하려 하는 거야!? 당장 내 앞에서 꺼져!\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">난... 너보다 훨씬 더 저 아이를 구하고 싶다고...</font>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Daniel！等等啦！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "對不起……我不知道我怎麼了，讓我一個人靜一靜。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "我陪你……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "我說讓我一個人啦！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊！Daniel……！哇！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳還好嗎？這不是 Clara 嗎？你們怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "不，沒事，我們來看 Aroma。來，你的電話，對不起。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "沒關係，小心點吶。\n"}, {"id": 